des: "Four ingredients and eight minutes are all you need to whip this dip together. Mix sour cream, green chiles and cubed cheese with McCormickÂ® Cheesy Taco Seasoning Mix. Bake until ooey-gooey and get to dipping with your favorite tortilla chips."
ins:
Mix all ingredients in large microwaveable bowl.
Microwave on HIGH 2 minutes. Stir. Microwave 1 minute longer or until heated through. Stir until smooth.
Serve hot with tortilla chips.
